data.name: lblLocations.ToolTip
data.value:
Directories where the game may be found on the user's computer. Use environment variables wherever possible. One location per line. Registry values can also be used.
Examples: %PROGRAMFILES(X86)%\Activision\Call of Duty 4 HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\Activision\Call of Duty 4\InstallDir

data.name: lblModules.ToolTip
data.value:
A comma-delimited list of modules to be used as launchers and injection targets. Infinity will consider the largest found module to be the injection target and the smallest found module to be the launcher.
Examples: game.exe, bin\Win32\launcher.exe
